mit, any such solution\napproaches the spatially homogeneous equilibrium $(\\hat{n},\\hat{m},\\hat{m},0)$\nin an appropriate sense, where\n$\\hat{n}=\\frac{1}{|\\Omega|}\\{\\int_{\\Omega}n_0-\\int_{\\Omega}m_0\\}_{+}$ and\n$\\hat{m}=\\frac{1}{|\\Omega|}\\{\\int_{\\Omega}m_0 -\\int_{\\Omega}n_0\\}_{+}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Jul 2019 01:08:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Aug 2019 07:23:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-05"}
