the complete graph on $n$ vertices, the null\ngraph on $n$ vertices, the disjoint union of the $K_2$ with $n-2$ isolated\nvertices ($n\\geq 2$), and the complete bipartite graph with parts of sizes $n$\nand $m$, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Jul 2019 08:38:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-30"}
